BamBam, one of the housemates of Ongoing TV reality show, BBNaija has been called upon by her parents to come home after she was caught on Camera having sex with another housemate, Teddy A on Tuesday morning. Fisayo Awonuga revealed this in a tweet she shared online. She revealed that BamBam’s parents are disappointed in their daughter. According to Fisayo who claimed to be a family friend to the family, the parents have met with Big Brother Naija organizers.  The parents want their daughter evicted from the show. It could be recalled that BamBam came from a religious family where her father is an elder in the church. She has been under fire for the act because of her religious background. It was gathered that she was an active choir member before she went for BBNaija show.
